data.title: The Best Music of 2025: Human Creativity in an AI World
data.description: As songs created by artificial intelligence become more common, the year’s best albums—from Rosalía, Geese, Wednesday and others—are a reminder of how music connects us to other people.
data.author: Mark Richardson
